    <section id="id8878628">
      <title>CHILDREN’S RIGHTS</title>
      <para id="id14757040"/>
      <section id="id8126345">
        <title>Children’s rights according to the South African constitution</title>
        <para id="id4056512">In module 4 you made posters on which you wrote the 12 rights and responsibilities of South African children. These posters can be put up in the classroom again. It is even possible that they were so attractive that they were never even taken down!</para>
        <para id="id18832118">In the first outcome we focused our attention on the rights that affect the health of our children. Now we are going to discuss all 12 of the rights and responsibilities.</para>
      </section>
