      <para id="id16269749">LEARNING OUTCOME 2: SOCIAL DEVELOPMENT</para>
      <para id="id15718008">The learner will be able to demonstrate an understanding of and commitment to constitutional rights and responsibilities, and to show an understanding of diverse cultures and religions.</para>
      <para id="id6565341">Assessment Standard</para>
      <para id="id9292278">We know this when the learner</para>
      <para id="id3579858">2.1 discusses children’s rights and responsibilities as stipulated in the South African Constitution.</para>
